**who —** The Energy Bottleneck — Nick Lane's argument that the merger broke a hard energy limit — energy per gene leapt, letting cells afford large genomes — and that this may be why complex life arose only once

**what —** Nick Lane's argument that the merger broke a hard energy limit — energy per gene leapt, letting cells afford large genomes — and that this may be why complex life arose only once

